    {
      "id": "tools_items",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 295,
      "y": 130,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 350,
      "text": "EstimateObjectDepth\n  DepthAnythingV2 (ViT-L)\n  → metric depth in meters\n\nEstimateOpticalFlow\n  RAFT\n  → flow vectors (dx, dy)\n\nGetObjectOrientation\n  OrientAnything (DINOv2)\n  → azimuth, polar, rotation angles\n\nGetCameraParametersVGGT\n  VGGT\n  → intrinsic K + extrinsic [R|t]\n\nEstimateHomographyMatrix\n  SIFT + RANSAC\n  → 3x3 transformation matrix\n\nGetObjectMask\n  SAM2\n  → pixel-level masks + areas",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 107,
      "version": 1,
